body_html:
I had the same problem, but could successfully compile the whole package with following quick fix. Please change ./tensorflow/core/platform/macros.h

from
#define TF_PREDICT_FALSE(x) (__builtin_expect(x, 0))
#define TF_PREDICT_TRUE(x) (__builtin_expect(!!(x), 1))

to

#define TF_PREDICT_FALSE(x) (x)
#define TF_PREDICT_TRUE(x) (x)

body:
I had the same problem, but could successfully compile the whole package with following quick fix. Please change ./tensorflow/core/platform/macros.h

from
#define TF_PREDICT_FALSE(x) (__builtin_expect(x, 0))
#define TF_PREDICT_TRUE(x) (__builtin_expect(!!(x), 1))

to

#define TF_PREDICT_FALSE(x) (x)
#define TF_PREDICT_TRUE(x) (x)
